{"tid":1928152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍出現首名懷疑艦上確診個案　感染士兵在家隔離","createTime":"2020-03-16T08:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T09:15:19.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9660f077101c9383830c72da6e79130ed628c0","tid":1928152,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍出現首名在艦上懷疑確診新型冠狀病毒個案，一名駐守兩棲攻擊艦拳師號的士兵，初步對病毒檢測呈陽性反應，最後結果有待衛生部門覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n美軍聲明說，這名士兵正在家隔離，已成功聯絡與他有密切接觸的人，他們亦在家自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n上星期一名駐守意大利南部的海軍士兵，曾經接觸病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514769-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514769-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2Bebf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b9336312\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514769-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=87f31d69\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514769-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c5395a7779a26b4e9e7577ccc07ae11a181968d4","tid":1928152,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"屌啊"},{"pid":"e9b4980889cb46b092b992dfc60acc1f95683fe7","tid":1928152,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"支那生化武器攻擊美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}